network_overview: The capture contains only two IP flows: a 3-packet TCP/80 exchange between private addresses and a single UDP packet between RFC-1918 space, with no 3GPP, IMS, or voice protocols present. No GTP, Diameter, PFCP, SIP, or RTP traffic is observable at this mirror point.

observations.finding: One 53-byte UDP packet sent from 10.0.0.1:5000 to 10.0.0.2:6000 with no reply captured
observations.evidence: UDP packet at 1768281044.21193 s, no return packet in capture
